{"id":368527,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":12}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"154","ytitle":"","mtitle":"农村短歌","ftitle":"","authors":["王肇岐"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海西郊诸翟乡陆家宅　王肇岐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑河泥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千担泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万担泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩桃河泥歌声起:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\05\\585c0304AA.JPG\">唷嗨呀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十斤肥料换斤米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑起河泥双脚飞!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花轿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭炮放，锣鼓敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社里来了大花轿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟看见双脚跳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟问爷爷:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今天谁家办喜事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是哪位大哥把新娘讨?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷听了哈哈笑:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“勿是人家有喜事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥娶亲也不用轿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叔伯生产超指标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"区里抬来光荣榜。”"}]}